fields.body:
The method inside the class social/storage/django_orm.py:

```
    @classmethod
    def get_users_by_email(cls, email):
        return cls.user_model().objects.filter(email=email)
```

should be:

```
    @classmethod
    def get_users_by_email(cls, email):
        return cls.user_model().objects.filter(email_iexact=email)
```

in order to avoid user duplication with same email when using a case sensitive collation (I'm using PostgreSQL).

